  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The equation above is true for all <span class=\"italic\">x</span>, where <span class=\"italic\">a</span> and <span class=\"italic\">b</span> are constants. What is the value of <span class=\"italic\">ab</span> ?</p>\n",
